+ Class Methods

++ Public

* Solar_App::__construct() -- Constructor.

* Solar_App::__get() -- Try to force users to define what their view variables are.

* Solar_App::__set() -- Try to force users to define what their view variables are.

* Solar_App::_setup() -- 

* Solar_App::addFlash() -- Appends a "read-once" session value for this class and key.

* Solar_App::apiVersion() -- Reports the API version for this class.

* Solar_App::display() -- Executes the requested action and displays its output.

* Solar_App::fetch() -- Executes the requested action and returns its output with layout.

* Solar_App::getFlash() -- Retrieves a "read-once" session value, thereby removing the value.

* Solar_App::locale() -- Looks up locale strings based on a key.

* Solar_App::setFlash() -- Sets a "read-once" session value for this class and a key.

++ Protected

* Solar_App::_actionFile() -- Returns the file name for an action.

* Solar_App::_collect() -- Collects action, pathinfo, and query values.

* Solar_App::_exception() -- Convenience method for returning exceptions with localized text.

* Solar_App::_forward() -- Forwards internally to another action.

* Solar_App::_info() -- Retrieve the TAINTED value of a pathinfo request key by name.

* Solar_App::_postAction() -- Executes just after the last action, and just before the view.

* Solar_App::_preAction() -- Executes just before the first action.

* Solar_App::_query() -- Retrieves the TAINTED value of a query request key by name.

* Solar_App::_redirect() -- Redirects to another page and action.

* Solar_App::_run() -- Includes a file in an isolated scope (but with access to $this).

++ Private

None.